{"tid":2386355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國Hanning電機 深圳設廠廿年 宣布1月底遷廠到印度","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T14:50:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2a8a34fd9c73943e708c0697f056aaf42adb2e","tid":2386355,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"德國老牌的德亨電機（品牌Hanning）在深圳製造業大本營龍崗區設廠生產20年後，宣佈1月底將打包走人，遷廠到印度。這是繼去年底美商精密製造史丹利百得、日商電子廠村田製作所關廠解散後，又一家龍頭外資撤離製造之都深圳。<br />\n<br />\n德亨電機深圳廠發佈通知，透露關廠原因是由於大陸貿易政策和供應商多方原因，導致成本增長，因此產品線將從深圳工廠全部打包，搬遷至印度工廠。而深圳廠房近千名工人將會就地遣散。<br />\n<br />\n有80年歷史、總部設在德國的德亨電機，是家電、工業自動化領域的電機製造巨頭，客戶遍布全球，僅在歐洲、中國、印度設四家分公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bannednews.org/2021/01/blog-post_295.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannednews.org%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_295.html&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH7%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=4a793eae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bannednews.org/2021/01/blog-post_295.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e9a13dbccd072bdc0fad94453cbfda428fed145","tid":2386355,"uid":152589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"走啦 廠踩廠啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16968af80d262bece45976b5163573d94026d9c4","tid":2386355,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"疫情直逼中南海 北京民眾寒冬中戶外檢測大排長龍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bannednews.org/2021/01/blog-post_453.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannednews.org%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_453.html&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH7%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=41b8f169\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bannednews.org/2021/01/blog-post_453.html</a><br />\n<br />\n對抗中共威脅 澳學者向美委員會提六建議<br />\n<br />\n<a h